1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 22=
(Sisters United)

3
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,840
Jinchen.

4
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:11,879
He Jinchen.

5
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,319
You trash!

6
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,439
Why is the model different?

7
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,599
Is the right key somewhere else?

8
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:32,240
These jewelry pieces...

9
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,840
Didn't I already sell them

10
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,680
and give the money to He Jinchuan?

11
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,120
Why did He Jinchen buy them back?

12
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,639
Found it.

13
00:03:59,199 --> 00:03:59,919
Right here.

14
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:13,840
Sis.

15
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,439
Since you found the key,

16
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,360
leave now.

17
00:04:17,639 --> 00:04:18,639
I'll put the key back for you.

18
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,360
Maybe I should stay here.

19
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:22,680
I'm not afraid of them.

20
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:24,000
I'm worried about you.

21
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,959
So even you look down on me?

22
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,680
I didn't mean it like that.

23
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:29,959
It's my own grudges,

24
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,319
only I can settle them.

25
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,040
No one else can do it for me.

26
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,639
You should go.

27
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,120
Never come back again.

28
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,920
Are you Su Li?

29
00:05:09,639 --> 00:05:10,399
He Jinchen,

30
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,600
you ignored me for years,

31
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,800
let the family bully me,

32
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:16,680
and yet

33
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:19,319
even you can be trapped by love.

34
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:20,920
Su Li.

35
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,360
Su Li.

36
00:05:23,519 --> 00:05:24,360
Su Li!

37
00:05:28,460 --> 00:05:29,680
(Engagement Banquet)

38
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,240
(Engagement Banquet)
Congratulations!

39
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:30,879
(Engagement Banquet)
Thank you.

40
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,639
This way, please.

41
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:34,079
Dad, where's Mom?

42
00:05:35,959 --> 00:05:37,560
You wouldn't even allow her to come

43
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,480
to my engagement banquet?

44
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,279
She's not feeling well.

45
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:42,240
Making her come all this way

46
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:43,439
would only make things worse.

47
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,839
But I really want her here.

48
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,360
I...

49
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,279
Miss He,

50
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,519
congratulations!

51
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:50,959
Thank you.

52
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,560
- Okay.
- This way, please.

53
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,199
This way, please.

54
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,860
(Mu Shaoze & He Jinxi
Engagement Banquet)

55
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,959
Welcome, distinguished guests,

56
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,600
to the engagement banquet
of Mr. Mu Shaoze

57
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:12,360
and Miss He Jinxi.

58
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,519
Now, please welcome
Mr. Mu Shaoze to the stage

59
00:06:15,639 --> 00:06:17,319
to share a few words.

60
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:20,879
Wonderful.

61
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:26,319
Thank you all for being here today.

62
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,560
I hereby announce

63
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:31,399
that I am calling off
my engagement to He Jinxi.

64
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:34,480
What? Call off?

65
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,600
Mu Shaoze!

66
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,800
Are you crazy?

67
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:45,480
How could you do this to my sister?

68
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,759
Call off the engagement?

69
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:53,720
It's all right.

70
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:54,879
Young people...

71
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:56,360
They are all like this.

72
00:06:57,879 --> 00:06:58,759
Just a little quarrel.

73
00:06:58,879 --> 00:06:59,480
It's fine.

74
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,720
I'm calling off the engagement

75
00:07:03,199 --> 00:07:04,079
because the He family

76
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,839
has no moral boundaries.

77
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,879
They have committed heinous acts.

78
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,600
I won't marry someone
from a family like that.

79
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,759
The He family's company,
Meiyan International,

80
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,439
produces beauty products

81
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:27,040
that contain excessive carcinogens.

82
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,199
This serum

83
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,079
killed my sister!

84
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:37,000
The He family and Meiyan International

85
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,439
must pay for what they've done!

86
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:39,839
Who is he?

87
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,720
Looks like he's causing trouble.

88
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,319
Why is he holding a portrait?

89
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,360
Everyone, listen to me,

90
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,720
Meiyan International...

91
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,519
Let me go!

92
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,439
What are you doing?

93
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,480
I want justice for my sister!

94
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,040
Let me go!

95
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,279
Let go!

96
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:54,680
I want justice for my sister!

97
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:55,600
Everyone...

98
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,480
Let me go!

99
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,480
That man was fired from our company,

100
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,439
so he holds a grudge.

101
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,920
Don't believe what he says.

102
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,519
Our beauty products

103
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,000
have unique formula.

104
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,000
They are safe and effective.

105
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,319
What is the unique formula?

106
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,120
Who is this?

107
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:13,519
The prohibited ingredient, TAF990?

108
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,600
Hello everyone.

109
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:24,040
I am Su Li, a journalist from Deep News.

110
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,600
They really look identical!

111
00:08:26,879 --> 00:08:28,560
She was the fake Madam Gu!

112
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,040
So she was a journalist!

113
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,839
According to our investigation,

114
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,799
the Meiyan serum's

115
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,759
so-called secret formula

116
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,600
is actually TAF990.

117
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,600
(Exposing the Whitening Scam)
It gives short-term results,

118
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,639
but long-term use ruins the skin

119
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:47,360
and may even cause cancer.

120
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,120
Cancer?

121
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,759
What do we do?

122
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,799
Previously,

123
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:54,000
Yunhu Resort

124
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,600
held a charity recovery program

125
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,840
for women whose skin was damaged

126
00:08:58,039 --> 00:08:59,519
after using Meiyan serum.

127
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,279
They are not the only victims.

128
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,120
Thousands of consumers are also at risk.

129
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:05,620
(Ingredient List)

130
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:07,300
(Victim List)

131
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,759
So many people!

132
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:09,840
Yes.

133
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,720
So many victims!

134
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,679
I used this too. What do I do?

135
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:17,720
These victims did try to fight back.

136
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,480
But every lawsuit, every report,

137
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,559
every attempt to defend their rights,

138
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,960
all were buried by the He family's money

139
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,240
and influence.

140
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,279
Their lawsuits failed.

141
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:29,200
In the end,

142
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:31,960
they suffer the physical damage
in silence.

143
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,480
Mr. He!

144
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,200
Mr. He!

145
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,480
Is this true?

146
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,759
Did you use prohibited ingredients?

147
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,679
These are all rumors!

148
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,399
All rumors!

149
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,559
We will definitely take legal action

150
00:09:44,639 --> 00:09:45,799
against those spreading lies.

151
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:49,240
We will give consumers

152
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,360
a proper explanation.

153
00:09:52,159 --> 00:09:52,679
Mr. He!

154
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,879
Mr. He! Mr. He!

155
00:09:53,879 --> 00:09:54,960
Don't leave!

156
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,840
What's going on?

157
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,240
Mr. He!

158
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:57,840
Mr. He!

159
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,440
Hurry!

160
00:10:02,039 --> 00:10:02,480
Go!

161
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:06,279
Mr. He, can you respond?

162
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:06,840
Mr. He!

163
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:08,759
Everyone,

164
00:10:09,919 --> 00:10:11,799
money can buy many things,

165
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,639
but it cannot buy the truth.

166
00:10:14,559 --> 00:10:15,759
Justice may be delayed,
but it will come.

167
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,000
To protect our own rights,

168
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:20,919
we must boycott these harmful products.

169
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:23,399
Let the truth be revealed to all.

170
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:26,080
Great!

171
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,320
Well said!

172
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:27,919
Well said!

173
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:28,840
Well said!

174
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,639
Jinxi,

175
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:41,960
where are you going?

176
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,159
I'm going to ask Mu Shaoze myself!

177
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:45,360
What's to ask?

178
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,200
In the end, it's because you're useless,

179
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,279
you can't even keep a man.

180
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:51,480
Mu Shaoze suddenly called it off!

181
00:10:51,679 --> 00:10:52,480
What did I do wrong?

182
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,960
I've already arranged
for you to study abroad.

183
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,120
You'll leave tomorrow.

184
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,360
Don't embarrass me here.

185
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,080
I'm not leaving!

186
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:00,799
Why should I leave?

187
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,240
You leave when I say so!

188
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:03,279
I'm the head of this family!

189
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,039
Dad!

190
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,240
You're even keeping Mom locked up

191
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:08,039
and now you're forcing me to leave!

192
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:10,279
Is there any humanity left in you?

193
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:11,279
Any love for your family?

194
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,440
Is that how you talk to me?

195
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:15,679
Remember,

196
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,519
you are my daughter.

197
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,720
I know you better than anyone.

198
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,320
I know everything.

199
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,919
If you hadn't schemed,

200
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,840
would Mu Shaoze have agreed
to marry you?

201
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,159
So you'd better know your place.

202
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,919
Without me,

203
00:11:30,159 --> 00:11:31,000
you are nothing.

204
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,279
Go back.

205
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:52,600
Here.

206
00:11:53,039 --> 00:11:53,519
Here.

207
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,559
Niannian,

208
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,279
we couldn't have made it without you.

209
00:11:59,679 --> 00:12:01,080
If you hadn't tipped us off,

210
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:01,799
I wouldn't have been able

211
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,200
to expose Meiyan International

212
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,320
and the He family's true colors

213
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,720
so smoothly at the engagement banquet.

214
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:07,960
If you hadn't convinced He Jinxi

215
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:10,120
to hold her banquet at my hotel,

216
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:12,440
I wouldn't have been able to help much.

217
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,759
Thank goodness you gave us

218
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:18,919
He Jinchuan's location,

219
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:21,120
so we could get those crucial leads.

220
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,639
With that little bit of money he has,

221
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:24,200
he'll blow through it in no time.

222
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,200
And let me tell you.

223
00:12:25,399 --> 00:12:26,759
He actually thinks I'll forgive him.

224
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:28,320
He's abroad

225
00:12:28,399 --> 00:12:30,000
and can barely manage his own life,

226
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,559
and he still had the time
to come after you?

227
00:12:33,679 --> 00:12:34,360
But

228
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,879
thinking back to how lovesick I was,

229
00:12:37,279 --> 00:12:38,159
it's pretty ridiculous.

230
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,279
There's nothing wrong

231
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,360
with loving someone with all your heart.

232
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:43,039
But you can't lose

233
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,039
your principles and boundaries for love.

234
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,240
You deserve better

235
00:12:47,519 --> 00:12:49,440
and you'll definitely be super happy.

236
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:50,840
Of course!

237
00:12:51,039 --> 00:12:53,720
Now my eyes can see through anything.

238
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:55,519
Like the Monkey King?

239
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:06,919
Mu Shaoze,

240
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,639
how dare you do this to me!

241
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,039
Don't you want the recording?

242
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,759
He Jinxi,

243
00:13:15,639 --> 00:13:16,879
your recording is just a fragment.

244
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:20,039
I have the full recording
from He Jinchuan now.

245
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,720
That useless fool.

246
00:13:25,399 --> 00:13:26,200
Shaoze,

247
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,759
can't you see

248
00:13:28,879 --> 00:13:30,519
that everything I did
was because I love you?

249
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,000
Can't you feel it?

250
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,039
Jinxi,

251
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,679
stop deceiving yourself.

252
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,399
You only love yourself.

253
00:13:37,919 --> 00:13:39,080
You just want to satisfy yourself.

254
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,440
Shaoze,

255
00:13:45,759 --> 00:13:47,120
I'm going abroad tomorrow.

256
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,200
I won't bother you anymore.

257
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:53,320
But please, help my mother.

258
00:13:53,559 --> 00:13:55,200
My father locked her up.

259
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:15,940
(Building emotion)

260
00:14:16,020 --> 00:14:17,700
(Thinking of unhappy things)

261
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:21,740
(So hard)

262
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:30,740
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

263
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:35,580
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

264
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:40,140
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

265
00:14:40,140 --> 00:14:45,060
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

266
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:48,860
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

267
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:53,660
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

268
00:14:53,660 --> 00:14:56,500
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

269
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:59,180
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

270
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:05,100
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

271
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:12,300
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

272
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:17,260
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

273
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:24,220
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

274
00:15:24,540 --> 00:15:31,340
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

275
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:36,020
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

276
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:39,380
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

277
00:15:39,380 --> 00:15:46,300
♪Right as I confess my love♪
